\id 2PE - Awajun-AT+NT publicado 
\h 2 Pedro 
\toc1 Pedro awentsaik carta agagbau 
\toc2 (2 Pedro) 
\toc3 2 P. 
\mt1 Pedro awentsaik carta agagbau 
\c 1  
\s1 Kumpamkagtamu 
\p  
\v 1 Witjai Simón Pedro, inakaitjai nuigtush Jesucristo apostoljiyaitjai, iina Apajuiji Uwemtijamin nuigtú Jesucristo pegkejan takauwa nu dekaskeapi tabau shiig pegkeg jutii ajutjama duke ajutjamu asagmin atumnash kumpamjime.  
\v 2 Iina Apají Apajuí, iina Apuji Jesusjai anenjauch wait anenjamag shiig agkan pujutan amastinme. Atumek ni pachisjumesh shiig dekau asagmin. 
\s1 Jesusan nemagkaju aidau pujumain 
\p  
\v 3 Apajuí niina senchijin ashí iina pujutjin atsumamua nuna nuigtú nigki puyatjusa umigta nunash sujamsauwai; nigki niina imanji nuigtú ni takasbauji shiig pegkeja nunash dekatnume tusa etegtamjauwai.  
\v 4 Nunú senchik ashí pegkeg tikichin nagkaesau aidaun ni anagtamauwa nunash sujamsauwai; dutikamu asag ju nugka jui pegkegchau wakegat aina nunak agkanmagawag Apajuí wajukuita imanuk atinme tujamu asa.  
\v 5 Nuadui atumshakam kakanmamainaitjume dekaskeapi tabauwa nu, pegkeg takamua dusha ajití tabaunum; pegkeg takamua nu, dekata dusha ajití;  
\v 6 dekata nu, iik kuitamamta dusha ajití; iik kuitamamta nu, waugtakchau ata dusha ajití; waugtakchau ata nu, Apajuí puyatjusa umigta dusha ajití;  
\v 7 Apajuí puyatjusa umigta nu, yatsut anendaisa anenita dusha ajití; yatsut anendaisa anenita nu, aneenit ajití. 
\p  
\v 8 Ashí ju aidau ajutjamainakuig nuigtush takamtikamak, nuní senchi iina Apuji Jesucristo dekatnum yaimpaktatjume, nuniau asajum atsumchataig nuigtú wainkagmek juwakchattagme.  
\v 9 Tujash juna betek uminachuk aents wainmachujai betekai, nuniachkush atushat wainmachua nuninai, yaunchuk tudauji aajakua nuna Apajuí tsagkujamunash aneachu asa.  
\v 10 Nuadui yatsug aidauh, atumek Apajuí untsukbau nuigtú etegkamu asajum nuig ebetmamata tabaunum kakanmamsatajum; wagki aaja nuniakjumek kakajus tudauk takaschattagme.  
\v 11 Nuniau asajum shiig anentsá, iina Apuji Uwemtikagtin Jesucristua nuna inamtaiji tuke atina nui awayam atatjume. 
\p  
\v 12 Nuadui junak tuke aneemtiksanké atatjime dekagminkish, nuigtú dekaskea nu atumin ajutjamjum nui ebetmamjau ainagminig.  
\v 13 Wi iwaaku pujag duik, tuke aneemtiksanké amainaitjim duka pegkejai.  
\v 14 Wagki dekajai dukap pujutsuk jakattag nunak, iina Apuji Jesucristo dekamtijuama nunisnuk.  
\v 15 Tujash ashí wi dutikmainnak dutiksan dekapsatjai, wi jakamtaish nunú aina nunak, tuke aneaku atinme tau asan. 
\s1 Cristo imanjin wainkaju aidau 
\p  
\v 16 Wagki iina Apuji Jesucristo ashí ni senchijijai minitna nu pachisa atum dekamtikauwaitag duka, aents anentaimsa augmattsamu aina nuninchauwai, duka iina jiin niina imanji wainkauwaitag nu tibaiji,  
\v 17 ni Apají Apajuiya nu eme anentus nuigtú tsaaptin ema awajus, nu tsaaptin shiig pegkeja nuiya chichaman akupjak: “Juuwai mina uchig anetaijuk, wi etegkamu”, tiuwa nu.  
\v 18 Nu chicham nayaimpinmayag jutii antukbaiji, niijai muja pegkegma nui batsamsaja. 
\p  
\v 19 Nuigtushkam chicham dekaskea nuna profeta aidau tibauwa nu ajutjamji, nunú emamkesjum dekatajum, dita chichakbauwa duka lámpara ekemakam suwen tsaaptin emama numamtinai, nunin asa Cristo yaya etsawamak tsaaptin wegama imana nu atumi anentaiminish tsaaptin etamtatui.  
\v 20 Tuja ashí dekatkau dekamainaitjum duka: Atak uminkatin chicham Agagbauwa duka, makichik aentskesh ni wajuk anentaimua nu tichamu ainawai,  
\v 21 nu atak uminkatin tibauwa duka, makichkish aents wakegak tibau ainatsui, duka aents pegkejam Apajuinu aajakajua nuna, Wakaní Pegkejiya nu ujaam tiaju ainawai. 
\c 2  
\s1 Maestro waitá jintin aidau 
\p  
\v 1 Israelnumash wait profeta aidaush aajakajui, atum ainajum nuish maestro waitá jintin aidau agtina nunisag. Ditak dekamainchaun jintidiagtinai ditá anentai pegkegchauwa nuiyan, aatus nuninak Apu Jesús ditan agkanmitkauwa nunash dakitiagtinai; nuninai pachiachbau dita bakumatnuji jegajiagtinai.  
\v 2 Kuashat saetukagtinai datsanmainun takaina nuna, nuninak dekaskea nunak pegkegchau chichajiagtinai.  
\v 3 Kuashat kuichik ajuttí tabaunum waitá jintinak jujutjabiagtinai; tujash dita bakumatna duka yaunchuk nagkamas umigkamui, dutikamu asamtai dita megkaekatna duka dakas ajawai. 
\p  
\v 4 Apajuik ángel aidau tunamakajunak tsagkuujachui, ayatak suwimak tuke atin suwea nui achijá utsauwai, tsawan jegatai suwimkan susata tau asa.  
\v 5 Nuigtushkam Apajuik yaunchuk aents ju nugka jui batsamajakajua nunakesh tsagkugtsuk, diluvio awetiuwai aents pegkegchau takau batsamajakajua nuna, dutikak Noé pegkejan chichagkagtujakua nunak, nuigtú siete aents aidaujai uwemtijauwai.  
\v 6 Aikasag yaakat aidau Sodoma nuigtú Gomorra aina nunak suwimkan suwak apekui, dutika yuku awajsauwai, nunak atak aents pegkegchau takaidau batsabiagtina dusha wainkatnume tusa iwainak dutikauwai,  
\v 7 tujash Lotnak pegkejan takau asamtai uwemtijauwai, aents pegkegchaun takagtai anentaimak waitujakua nuna,  
\v 8 wagki nunú aents pegkejan takau ditajai ijunag pujujakua duka, pegkejan anentaima nunak waitiau kashí kashinig pegkegchau takagtai wainak nuigtush antau asa. 
\p  
\v 9 Apu Apajuik niina puyatjus umijuina nunú utugchatnum jegatai agkanmitkatnak dekawai, dutikak aents pegkegchau takaidaunak ayatak kuitamui tsawan jegatai suwimkan susamig tusa,  
\v 10 nunak iyashí pegkegchau wakega nunak takainak, ni inabaujiya nunash wainkaya nunin diina nuna dutikatnai. Nunú aina duka antumtikmainchau nuigtush emebau asag, senchigtin wagaaku aina nu pegkegchau chichagtanash ishamainatsui,  
\v 11 nuninai, ángel ditá nagkaesau dekas senchigtin aina dukesh, dita suwimak jukitnun pachisagkesh pegkegchauk chichajuinatsui Apu Apajuí eemtinish. 
\p  
\v 12 Tujash nunú aents aidauk ditakesh antachiatak wají pegkegchau aidaun chichainawai; ditak kuntin anentainchau ayatak akiinawag maam megkaega nuniktin ainawai,  
\v 13 dita pegkegchau takasbaujin suwimkan juinak. Nunú aidauk pegkegchau nuigtú tsuwapaekau ainawai, nunin aidau atumjai ijunag yuinak shiig anenawai ditá pegkegchauji aina nujai. 
\p  
\v 14 Nuwa aidaunash tsanijimat anentaiyai dii yujau ainawai, nunidau asag tudau takatnash yawetuinatsui; nunisag aents imagnis Cristun nemajuinatsu nunash tsanú yujainawai, pegkegchau aidau wakeeta nunak unuimatjau asag, tikima aents pegkegchau ainawai.  
\v 15 Ditak pegkeg takatnak idaisag, Balaam Bosora uchijí nunikua nuna wejuinak dewakaje, duka pegkegchau takaamujin akiam atatus wakegajakui,  
\v 16 nuniau ni pegkegchaujinig jiyankauwai; makichik burro kijin aentsmitkatai, chichachuitak, aentstijai betek chichakui, dutikak profeta anentaimkas nuniamujin idaimitkasui. 
\p  
\v 17 Nunú aidauk yumigmat kuyuauwa nunin ainawai, yujagmin dase umpui juwama numamtin, nunú aidau batsamsati tibauk shiig suwe kanchi wajas awa nuuwai.  
\v 18 Ditak ememas chichainak nuigtush wainak chichau ainawai; nuninak wakegat pegkegchaun iyashnum takanitan anentain egketin ainawai, aents yamá pegkegchaujin idaiyas pujuina nuna.  
\v 19 Nuninak anagkuinawai agkan pujuta nuna, pegkegchau takatnum achikbau ainayatak; wagki ashí achikbau aina duka depetkamu asa nuniawai  
\v 20 Jutii Apuji Jesucristo Uwemtikagtina nuna nemajak, pegkegchau ju nugkanmaya takatan idaisauwaitak, ataktú dita takajakbaujin waketjuinakug, depetkamu weawai, nuniau asa yaunchuk aajakbaun nagkaesau pegkegchau weawai. 
\p  
\v 21 Ditak imá pegkeg takat pegkeja nunak dekamainchaunas dekau aajabiatai, chicham pegkejam umiktin susamua nuna dekauwaitak idaiyina nunitsuk.  
\v 22 Tujash ditai proverbionum dekas tawa duka uminui: “Yawak iyakbaujin pempeentinai, kuchi imaimush kuchan tadaetinai”, tawa nu. 
\c 3  
\s1 Jesucristo minitnuji 
\p  
\v 1 Aneetaig aidauh, juuwai carta awentsanuk agatjim nu. Nunú mai agagbauwa nuig wakekajai, shiig anentaimtijatasan taja dui ayatak pegkegnak anentaimainak,  
\v 2 profeta pegkejam aidau tibauwa nuna adeagtinme, nuigtú chicham umiktinun Apu Uwemtikagtin tibaun apóstol aidau sujamsamua nuna tusan. 
\p  
\v 3 Dekas dekatkauk ju dekamain ainagme, tsawan nagkantina duik, iyash pegkegchau wakegamujin takamtikin aina nu, dushiktamas chichagtamainak  
\v 4 tiagtinai: “¿Taatnaitjai tusa anagkagtuauwa dusha wajukae? Wagki iina muunji jinawagmataish, ashí wají nagkamsa najankamua duka yamaikish nunisag ainajama” tusag. 
\p  
\v 5 Nunú aents aidauk, yaunchuk tsawan aajakua imanui nagkamas Apajuí nayaimpin najana niina chichamenig nugkan yuminmaya akankamu, yuminmag egketka nunak tuke aneas dekachu wajukmaina nuninawai.  
\v 6 Yaunchuk Apajuí yumin yutumtikag ashí nugkan amugmatai, aents nui batsamajakui duka ashí jinawajui.  
\v 7 Tujash nayaim, nugka yamai aina juka, niina chichamenig esaktin kuitamkam awai. Nunú jiiya nu apeatnai aents pegkegchau takau aidau suwimak suwamu tsawan jegatna dui. 
\p  
\v 8 Tujash kajimatkigpa aneetaig aidauh, Apu Apajuiyaig makichik tsawantak mil mijana nuninai, tuja mil mijanak makichik tsawanta nuninai.  
\v 9 Apu Apajuik ni anagkagtuamujinak umitskek idaisashtatui, ujumak aents taashtina nunin anentaimtuina nunak, nuninaitak nigka waugtuk dutikchauwa dui, makichkish megkaekashtinme, ayatak pujutjin yapajiatnume tusa aniawai. 
\s1 Yamajam nayaim, yamajam nugka 
\p  
\v 10 Tujash Apu Jesús minamuk kasa pachiachbau kashi miniyama numamtuk atinai; nu tsawantinig nayaim aidauk shiig ishamainun kedegtuk megkaegainai, nui ayá dushakam esakag yuku waigkagtinai, antsag nugkashkam ashí nui takasbau ayá dushakam esakagtinai. 
\p  
\v 11 Ashí nunú aidauk aatus utsankagtin asamtai, atumek pegké pujakjum, puyatjusjum umigmainaitjume,  
\v 12 nuniakjum shiig senchi wakejusjum tsawan Apajuí minitnujiya nu dakastajum. Nu tsawantinig nayaim aidauk jiiyai apekbau atinai, tuja nui ayá dushakam jii keetai yumimeakag megkaejagtinai.  
\v 13 Tujash jutiik, ni anagtamamu yamajam nayaim aidau nuigtú yamajam nugka nu dakainaji, ayatak pegkejak takaamu atina nu. 
\p  
\v 14 Nuadui aneetaig aidauh, nunú nuniktina nu dakainakjum, kakanmamsatajum niina emtin shiig agkan pujakjum, pegkegchau atsugbau nuigtú nuninai tusaish tumainchau wantinkamnujum.  
\v 15 Adeagtajum iina Apuji emamkemas dakama nunak, uwemjatnume tabaunum aniawai. Juna pachis iina aneetaiji yatsug Pabloshkam, Apajuí dekat susamua dui agaje,  
\v 16 ashí ni carta agagbauwa nuig juna pachis chichawai, nunú aina nuiya shiig antumainchaush aina nuna, aents dekachu aidau nuigtú ebetmamjachu aina nu yajupenawai, dutiksag tikich agagbau aina nunash dutikaidau asag, dita bakumatnujin umigmamainawai. 
\p  
\v 17 Nuadui aneetaig aidauh, atumek emtika dekau asajum kuitamamkatajum, aents pegkegchau aina nu tsanugmajagmatai wejakjum, atum ebetmamja pujamu idaisaijum.  
\v 18 Nunitsuk, dekas tsakagtajum anentag jukimua nui nuigtú iina Apuji Jesucristo Uwemtikagtina nu dekatnum, nigki yamaish nuigtú tuke pujustin tsawan jegatna nuish ememattai atí. 
\p Aatus atí.